  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nThe [Cancel] and [Join] buttons are out of the screen for some devices on the 'Join Community' overlay\r\n\r\n**Preconditions:**\r\nUser didn't join to the status community yet\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Go to the communities page\r\n2. Tap 'Opened' tab\r\n3. Tap Status\r\n4. Tap [Join Community] button\r\n5. Check opened 'Join Community' overlay\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[Cancel] and [Join] buttons  are hidden\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/216070723-ee95f721-0ac5-4a56-b69a-571ef623d636.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[Cancel] and [Join] buttons  are shown\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/216071027-4c1334cf-0850-4119-b08e-f236db959763.png)\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n- Status version: nightly 1 Feb 2023 [2612]\r\n- Operating System: Android version 9, Huawei P20 light\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
